        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Protecting Americans Safety, Security, and Privacy Over Repressive Tyranny Act or the Passport Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits the use of federal funds to support any system that requires individuals to provide documentation of their vaccination status in order to travel, attend an event, or conduct other activities.</p>]]>
        </text>
